rComments: Really awesome, very sweet, understanding and supportive. All-time favorite prof.

Rima is the nicest person in the world, and incredibly socially aware. She is sensitive to everyone's needs, steps in when discussions in class get heated, and makes a point of educating people instead of yelling at them if they slip up. Her class was the most inclusive class I've ever been in, and she presents the material clearly. She's the best!

Amazing Professor! Took three classes with her, this, and HIS366 and HIS367. The class is never boring, she engages the class in discussions that are always interesting. She is the nicest and most helpful prof and definitely one of the best classes I have taken throughout University.

The best prof I've ever had. Classes are more than interesting, prof is the most approachable and helpful one you could wish for. Anyone who has the opportunity should take any of her courses, they are all simply great.
